title: Please identify this condensed face / 'Theta': narrow stressed sans
content:
I need to identify this face. I have tried Expel as well as Empire. Both are close, but neither match the "A". Specifically, the top of the "A" where the letter becomes thinner. Expel is the closest match I have. Was wondering if anyone could get an exact match.
